data.description: This 3 bedroom ranch home offers all the space you need for comfortable living! The covered front porch welcomes you and invites you inside to the living room complete with a big picture window. In the spacious kitchen, you'll find durable vinyl plank flooring, space for dining and appliances that are negotiable with the sale. Down the hall are three bedrooms, including the master with a convenient half bath as well as the main full bath with a tub and shower surround. The laundry area and an abundance of storage space can be found in the full unfinished basement. Outside, you'll appreciate the large fully fenced backyard with a shed for outdoor lawn equipment and toys. Recent updates include a new A/C and water heater. This affordable home is tucked in a neighborhood yet close to the hospital, parks and downtown Orville.  Call to schedule your showing today!
